parameters.name: InstanceId
parameters.description: The ID of the instance whose fine-grained monitoring configurations you want to query.

parameters.name: InstanceType
parameters.description: The type of the instance. Set the value to **EIP**.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description:
The region ID of the instance.

You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~36063~~) operation to query the most recent region list.
